cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with word embeddings and language analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new heuristic to train temporal word embeddings based on the Word2vec model. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of temporal word embeddings to study the evolution of languages. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to generate vector representations of words. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the efficiency of the training process used in temporal word embeddings.
